data.description: Currently occupied but will be a Nice move in ready single story home with 3 bedrooms plus an office that was built in 2016. Ceramic tile flooring throughout the whole house for easy care maintenance! Recent interior paint throughout house. Open floor plan with office that could also be extra den or dining area. Master bath has double vanity and master has walk in closet. Some upgrades include gutters, sprinkler system, water softener system w/ reverse osmosis, radiant barrier roofing decking, and so much more! Close to Lackland AFB.
